abcd\"</span>),\n    strcmp(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"abc\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"abc\"</span>)\n</code></pre>\n<p><br><br>\n함수 반환 예시</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs lang-py\">\n    <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>\n    -<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>\n    -<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n</code></pre>\n<br>\n<br>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs lang-py\">\n<span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">strcmp</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\">s1, s2</span>):</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"\"\"\n    s1 > s2일 경우, 1 반환\n    s1 == s2일 경우, 0 반환\n    s1 &#x3C; s2일 경우, -1 반환\n    \"\"\"</span>\n    \n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">##### 두 문자열이 일치하는 경우 #####</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">len</span>(s1) == <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">and</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">len</span>(s2) == <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>:\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># ???</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">#####################################</span>\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">##### 한 문자열이 다른 문자열의 앞부분만 일치하는 경우 #####</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">elif</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">len</span>(s1) == <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>:\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># ???</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">elif</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">len</span>(s2) == <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>:\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># ???</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">############################################################</span>\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">##### 특정 인덱스의 문자가 일치하지 않는 경우 #####</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">elif</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">ord</span>(s1[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>]) > <span class=\"